cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.SD

This paper investigates the internal representations used by a recurrent neural network (RNN) to recognize a regular formal language. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SD).
